    • getRenderTypes

      public ChunkRenderTypeSet getRenderTypes(@NotNull @NotNull BlockState state, @NotNull @NotNull RandomSource rand, @NotNull ModelData data)
      Description copied from interface: IForgeBakedModel
      Gets the set of render types to use when drawing this block in the level. Supported types are those returned by RenderType.chunkBufferLayers().

      By default, defers query to ItemBlockRenderTypes.

      Specified by:
      getRenderTypes in interface IForgeBakedModel

    • getRenderTypes

      public List<RenderType> getRenderTypes(ItemStack itemStack, boolean fabulous)
      Description copied from interface: IForgeBakedModel
      Gets an ordered list of render types to use when drawing this item. All render types using the DefaultVertexFormat.NEW_ENTITY format are supported.

      This method will only be called on the models returned by IForgeBakedModel.getRenderPasses(ItemStack, boolean).

      By default, defers query to ItemBlockRenderTypes.

      Specified by:
      getRenderTypes in interface IForgeBakedModel
